1. What is CSS and how to add css to html ?
                 or
2. What are the types of CSS ?

# CSS Stands Cascading Stylesheet which is used to design HTML.
There are 3 ways : 1.Inline CSS
                   2.Internal CSS
                   3.External CSS

# In HTML we have 2 types of elements.
1.Inline-level Elements(tags)----->Will be displayed in the same line and CSS properties will be applied only to the content.

2.Block-level Elements(tags)----->Always displayed in the different line and CSS properties will be applied to the whole Block.
